    <Statements>
      <Statement> Describe events as subsets of a sample space (the set of outcomes) using characteristics (or categories) of the outcomes, or as unions, intersections, or complements of other events (&amp;ldquo;or,&amp;rdquo; &amp;ldquo;and,&amp;rdquo; &amp;ldquo;not&amp;rdquo;).</Statement>
