    </StatementCodes>
    <Statements>
      <Statement> Recognize and explain the concepts of conditional probability and independence in everyday language and everyday situations. &lt;i&gt;For example, compare the chance of having lung cancer if you are a smoker with the chance of being a smoker if you have lung cancer.&lt;/i&gt;</Statement>
